        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/4bbf92/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-11-24T21:59:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Best QPR for an 08 I\u2019ve tried to date.  From what I\u2019ve read 08 supposed to be a pinot vintage but damn this is still a fine champagne.  Beautiful fruit and balance, fruit not as buried as some of the other 08\u2019s that I\u2019ve tried, juicy acidity, seems mid dosage in terms of balance, lip smacking good right now and will effortlessly age for the mid term.  As close to the 08 Salon as I\u2019ll be owning.</p>",
